emuInput.TitMainTitle: Portrait of Delores Woodfork wearing scoop neck dress with gathers at neckline and beaded earrings, seated next to desk with wooden statue, another pose
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 21, 1963, pg. 16 reads: "Dynamic Danettes - Voicing their intention to make each one of their club members an NAACP life member, the Dynamic Danet[t]es Civic CLub is busy making plans to raise more funds. Left to right: Treasurer Margaret Nelson, General Chairman Florence Hutchinson, Secretary Gladys Brown, Audelle Wade, Delores Woodfork, Vice President Gladys Lawson, Betty Culberson, Jesse Grogan and President Ida Jones. - Harris Photos."
